OL,3,CCouncillors 'undecided' on plans for
OL,4,CNational Park
OL,6,FCouncillors in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,7,Fhave confirmed they are "undecided" as
OL,8,Fto whether plans for a national park
OL,9,Fin the area should go ahead.
OL,11,FThe proposals for a park in Galloway
OL,12,Fhas caused controversy among residents
OL,13,Fand campaigners on both sides turned
OL,14,Fup to a full council meeting on
OL,15,FWednesday (5 February) night to voice
OL,16,Ftheir concerns and opinions.
