OL,3,CCouncillors 'undecided' on plans for
OL,4,CNational Park
OL,6,FOver the past couple of months,
OL,7,FScottish public body Nature Scot has
OL,8,Fbeen carrying out a consultation of
OL,9,Flocal people and businesses to find
OL,10,Fout views on creating the park. The
OL,11,Fconsultation fed back to Dumfries and
OL,12,FGalloway councillors, who responded to
OL,13,Fit in the meeting.
OL,15,FA crucial part of a report prepared
OL,16,Ffor the meeting was the question: "to
OL,17,Fwhat extent do councillors support
OL,18,Fplans to create a new national park?"
