OL,3,CCouncillors 'undecided' on plans for
OL,4,CNational Park
OL,6,FCouncillors voted they were
OL,7,F"undecided" with no councillor voting
OL,8,Fagainst the plans - much to the
OL,9,Fencouragement of campaigners who want
OL,10,Fthe park in the area.
OL,12,FThose in the meeting, which was
OL,13,Fattended by ITV Border, felt that they
OL,14,Fdid not have enough information to
OL,15,Fmake a decision on the plans. This
OL,16,Fincluded a lack of information on
OL,17,Fwhere exactly the park would be
OL,18,Fcreated, as well as how it would be
OL,19,Ffunded or resourced.
