OL,3,CCouncillors 'undecided' on plans for
OL,4,CNational Park
OL,6,FCampaigners against the plans gathered
OL,7,Fahead of the meeting to voice their
OL,8,Fanger at the proposals. They are
OL,9,Fagainst the park for various reasons,
OL,10,Fincluding the possibility of it
OL,11,Fdriving up house prices in the area
OL,12,Fand bringing in too many visitors.
OL,14,FThose for the park say it would bring
OL,15,Fin tourists which would in turn boost
OL,16,Fthe local economy.
