OL,3,CCouncillors 'undecided' on plans for
OL,4,CNational Park
OL,6,FNature Scot will report on the
OL,7,Fconsultation to Scottish government
OL,8,Fministers at the end of April. If they
OL,9,Fdecide to proceed, Nature Scot will
OL,10,Fcarry out another consultation before
OL,11,Fa final decision is then made on the
OL,12,Fpark.
OL,14,FUltimately it is down to the Scottish
OL,15,Fgovernment to decide whether the
OL,16,Fnational park will go ahead.
